Text-CSV-Separator
==================

Description
-----------
This module provides a fast detection of the field separator character of a
CSV file.

Prerequisites
--------------
perl 5.008


Installation
------------
To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

In Windows systems, use nmake or dmake instead.


